model

Class Vertice<V1,V2>

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Vertice<V1,V2>

  • public class Vertice<V1,V2>
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that holds a vertice from the paparazzi map. A vertice consists of a child cell, a parent cell and the costs from cell to cell.
